info.author: Kuaishou AI Platform & DS3 Lab
info.name: bagua-cuda111
info.summary: Bagua is a deep learning training acceleration framework for PyTorch. It provides a one-stop training acceleration solution, including faster distributed training compared to PyTorch DDP, faster dataloader, kernel fusion, and more.
